creatives.headline: Uncover the Dark Truth: Cambodia's Horror Story
creatives.description: Witness the brutal reality of Cambodia's communist revolution, which claimed the lives of 25% of its population. Discover how Pol Pot's radical regime wiped out everything from money to toys, plunging the country into a new dark age. Hear firsthand accounts of survivors and learn how Paul Pot built over 100 concentration camps filled with unspeakable horrors. Don't miss this eye-opening video.
